Module simplehttpserver
Package com.kttdevelopment.simplehttpserver.handler

Class TemporaryHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kttdevelopment.simplehttpserver.handler.TemporaryHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HttpHandler
    public class TemporaryHandler
extends Object
implements HttpHandler
    A temporary handler handles a single request and then removes itself from the server. This can be used for single use downloads, or media file hosting. For time based expiry the handler will only remove itself if a user connects to the handler after the time expires.
    Since:
    03.03.00
